  "description": "This individual is a human woman of early middle years, defined by steady brown eyes and a compact, work-hardened build. Brown hair, worn in a plain style, frames a square face marked by fine lines at the mouth from habitual, practiced speech. Bronze skin and strong hands with thickened knuckles record long service in close quarters and constant handling of glass and cask. Her bearing remains composed and appraising, with an economy of motion characteristic of experienced canteen staff.",
